item.title: You Won't Believe How Much It Costs to Fix an iPhone 11 Pro Max Screen at the Apple Store!
item.description: Introduction If you’ve ever owned an iPhone, you know how expensive it can be to repair. But did you know that fixing an iPhone 11 Pro Max screen at the Apple Store could cost you up to $329? In this article, we’ll take a look at why the repair cost is so high and provide some alternatives to consider. Overview of the Cost of Repairing an iPhone 11 Pro Max Screen The cost of fixing an iPhone 11 Pro Max screen at the Apple Store is $329.
